[Meta]
RootName: @agender.sourceforge.net/agender:@VERSION@
DisplayName: Agender
ShortName: agender
Maintainer: Gabriel Espinoza <virtuosonic@users.sourceforge.net>
Packager: Gabriel Espinoza <virtuosonic@users.sourceforge.net>
Summary: Agender is a cross-plataform schedule tool
URL: http://agender.sourceforge.net/
License: GPLv3+
SoftwareVersion: @VERSION@
Repository: http://agender.sourceforge.net/autopackage/agender.xml
PackageVersion: 1
AutopackageTarget: 1.4

[Description]
Agender is a small cross-platform schedule tool where you asociate some notes
with a date or with no date in particular if  you mark the note as sticky, you
simply start it  and it will create a taskbar icon and stay in the background,
without anoying you,it can also be configured to run on login.

[BuildPrepare]
prepareBuild

[BuildUnprepare]
unprepareBuild

[Globals]


[Imports]
echo '*' | import

[Prepare]
require @wxwidgets.org/wxgtk 28
removeOwningPackage $PREFIX/bin/Agender

[Install]
installExe bin/*
installMenuItem "Calendar/Utility" share/applications/*
installIcon share/pixmaps/*
installLocale share/locale/

[Uninstall]
uninstallFromLog
